&lt;p&gt;St John’s Medical Centre are currently recruiting for a Salaried GP (with a view to partnership) to join our friendly Team, with the successful candiate offering 6 sessions per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a fast paced surgery and currently have a list size of approx 14,500.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In our latest annual CQC regulatory review we retained our rating of &#39;Good&#39;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a training practice, and currently have 2 GP Trainees working with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our large clinical team currently consists of 6 GP’s, 2 GP trainee, 2 Clinical Pharmacists, 3 Nurse Practitioners, 3 Home Visiting Nurses, 4 Practice Nurses, 4 Health Care Assistants, and a Diabetes Nurse. Amongst these team members, there are clinical interests in diabetes, respiratory disease, dermatology, sexual health and musculoskeletal conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in this position and would like to arrange an informal chat or have any questions regarding the position, please contact Lauren Fern, HR Manager on 01476 858820.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We reserve the right to close the advert early if we recieve a high number of applicants.&lt;/p&gt;
